  "_note": "Pure reference lookup, reads artifact.data (MasonStuff channel). application → mix table: general/veneer Type N (750 psi), structural Type S (1800 psi), high-strength Type M (2500 psi), repoint Type O (350 psi). Unknown application → general (Type N). Result card renders type/ratio/strength/use/waterRatio/cureTime/temperature EXACTLY."
